# `page.tsx` structure (design showcase)

Follow `guideline_to_page_prompt.md`:

- Define a `cssStyles` string with **tokens extracted from `guidelines.md`** (colors, typography, spacing, radius, shadows, timings).
- Render with:
  - `<style>{cssStyles}</style>`
  - `<main className="showcase">...</main>` (or equivalent scoped wrapper)

## Required sections (order matters)

1. Hero header (title, tagline, primary CTA)
2. Color palette (grouped swatches: base / accent / semantic)
3. Typography scale (headings + body variants + paragraph sample)
4. Buttons & interactive (primary/secondary/success/disabled + link style)
5. Cards (3+ cards; hover behavior per guidelines)
6. Form elements (input, error input, toggle/checkbox, select, submit)
7. Feedback & status (success/error/warning/info + progress ~65%)
